4.text:
Mystery wanderer, he was, in the Ghost World;

He was valuable in his own way;

Ghost World lies in India;

In his form, life is but a sunlit moment;

For the film, necessary is approval and success;

Some people abandon their ego and many sleepless nights.

6.text:
The mystery unfolded, there were clues on its path;

Their form was a tree bound by the sun in the time of life;

For a film, both the approver and success are necessary;

Only people had let go of their ego and slept under some trees.
